Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.31,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:293564,295316}Let's save this for later.{NOTE:話はあと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.90,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:295316,296901}A meal comes first.{NOTE:まずは腹ごしらえだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.03,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:300530,302031}Ebon Riders?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.36,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:302031,303366}That's right.{NOTE:そうです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:07.49,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:303366,307495}They're evil Riders who are robbing other Riders' of their Kinship Stones.{NOTE:他のライダーの絆石を奪っている悪いライダーたちです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:10.03,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:307495,310039}I haven't seen such Riders.{NOTE:そういったライダー集団は見ていない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.79,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:310706,312792}Can you recall any suspicious buildings?{NOTE:何か怪しい建物とかは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.91,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:312792,313918}Nope.{NOTE:いや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.29,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:313918,315294}I see.{NOTE:そうですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.42,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:316128,317421}Cheval…{NOTE:シュヴァルさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:21.96,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:317421,321968}Perhaps the Ebon Riders' hideout is outside desert zone after all?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズのアジトは砂漠地帯ではないのかもしれませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.92,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:321968,322927}Yup.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:27.93,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:323344,327932}I'll let the Royal Scriveners know as soon as I notice anything suspicious.{NOTE:もし何かそういったものを見掛けたら書士隊に伝えておくよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.51,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:328599,329517}Thanks.{NOTE:お願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.89,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:331143,332895}I'd like to ask you another question.{NOTE:それとは別のことなんですが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.31,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:334230,337316}Perhaps you've seen any Nargacuga around here?{NOTE:この辺りでナルガクルガを見ませんでしたか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.65,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:337316,338651}A Nargacuga?{NOTE:ナルガクルガ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:39.73,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:338651,339735}Yes.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.90,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:339735,341904}My Monstie's a Nargacuga.{NOTE:俺のオトモンのナルガクルガです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.99,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:341904,343990}I haven't seen any.{NOTE:見てはいないが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:44.94,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:343990,344949}Did it stray?{NOTE:はぐれたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:46.61,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:345867,346617}No…{NOTE:いえ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.03,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:347869,350037}I have done terrible thing to him.{NOTE:俺がひどいことをしてしまったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.91,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:351414,352915}Dark Thrash!{NOTE:スパイラルエッジ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.42,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:363509,364427}Heh.{NOTE:フッ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.89,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:371601,372894}Why, you…{NOTE:こいつ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.02,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:372894,375021}After it! Get it, Nargacuga!{NOTE:追え！やっつけろナルガクルガ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.36,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:379942,382361}What are you doing?!{NOTE:何してる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.82,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:382361,383821}Run!{NOTE:走れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.69,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:383821,385698}Run, you slowpoke!{NOTE:走れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.11,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:385698,387116}After it, Nargacuga!{NOTE:追えナルガクルガ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.83,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:395791,396834}You, too, huh?{NOTE:お前もか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.62,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:397668,399629}Another useless Monstie!{NOTE:お前も使えないオトモンか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.92,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:401714,403925}I don't need you, either.{NOTE:お前もいらない…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.63,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:403925,405635}Get out of here.{NOTE:どこかへ行っちまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.64,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:414060,415645}That's a sad story.{NOTE:そういうことか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.06,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:417188,418064}Yes.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:02.77,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:418773,422777}At that time, I was just looking for ways to acquire new strength.{NOTE:あのときの俺はただ強さだけを追い求めていて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:07.40,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:423486,427406}Your heart was caught in darkness.{NOTE:お前心を闇にとらわれていたんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:08.49,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:427782,428491}In darkness…?{NOTE:闇に？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.45,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:430701,432453}You're right.{NOTE:そうですね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:16.41,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:432453,436415}I lost myself and felt into darkness.{NOTE:深い闇の中に自分から落ちていったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:22.67,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:437875,442672}I would never have guessed you were doing such things to Monsties, Cheval.{NOTE:シュヴァルさんがオトモンにそんなことをしたなんて知りませんでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:26.00,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:443339,446008}Did you come to dislike me?{NOTE:俺と一緒にいるの嫌になった？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.21,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:446008,447218}No, not at all.{NOTE:いえいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.01,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:447218,449011}As if.{NOTE:まさかそんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:33.09,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:449011,453099}What I wanted to say is that I can hardly believe that person was you, Cheval.{NOTE:今のシュヴァルさんからはとても信じられないと言っているだけです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.89,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:454058,456894}How did you escape that darkness?{NOTE:お前はどうやってその闇から抜け出した？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.60,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:456894,457603}Ah.{NOTE:あっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.60,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:457603,458604}Right…{NOTE:はい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.61,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:464860,466612}Lute and Ratha.{NOTE:リュートやレイア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.23,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:466612,468239}My friends…{NOTE:仲間たちが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.32,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:468239,470324}…opened my eyes for me.{NOTE:俺の目を覚ましてくれました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:55.32,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:471534,475329}You came back from the darkness thanks to your friends, huh?{NOTE:闇の中から仲間たちの元へ戻ったということか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.58,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:476372,477581}That's correct.{NOTE:そうですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:07.71,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:483629,487717}They've chased the darkness away with their light.{NOTE:闇の中の俺にみんなが光を照らしてくれたんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.72,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:490219,492722}Nargacugas don't live in deserts.{NOTE:砂漠はナルガクルガのすみかではない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.30,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:493097,494306}Eh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:18.35,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:494306,498352}My guess is that an abandoned Nargacuga would return to its birthplace.{NOTE:捨てられたﾅﾙｶﾞｸﾙｶﾞは生まれた場所に戻ったんじゃないかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.22,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:498352,499228}Ah…{NOTE:あっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.98,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:500229,501981}If it manged to stay alive, that is.{NOTE:生き延びているのなら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.99,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:512533,514994}Ah. How annoying, how annoying.{NOTE:ああ、いまいましい、いまいましい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:38.49,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:515870,518497}Ah. How irritating. How aggravating.{NOTE:ああ、腹立たしい、腹立たしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.50,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:519331,522501}It's his fault that we still can't find Lute.{NOTE:リュートの行方が見つからないのはあいつのせいだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.58,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:522918,524587}Mad is disgusting.{NOTE:マッドは鼻につくし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.00,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:524587,526005}Wrath is dead stupid.{NOTE:ラースはおバカ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:50.00,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:527006,530009}We can't find him because he went into hiding.{NOTE:あいつがこそこそ隠れているから見つからない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.26,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:530718,533262}Gale is cheeky and self-centered.{NOTE:ゲイルは生意気で勝手ばかりだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.93,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:533804,535931}"It's not my fault", he says!{NOTE:あたしらのせいじゃないっての。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.81,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:536724,539810}Am I really the only reliable member in our group?!{NOTE:四天王で使えるのはあたしらだけじゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.14,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:539810,542146}When I'm in such a bad mood…{NOTE:こんなむしゃくしゃしたときは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.48,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:543773,545483}…it's time to hunt.{NOTE:狩りだよねぇ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.86,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:548944,549862}This is the place.{NOTE:この辺りだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.45,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:552156,554450}This is where I bonded with him.{NOTE:あいつをオトモンにしたのは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.95,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:554450,557953}It seems that this forest is home to many monsters.{NOTE:この森はモンスターが色々とすんでいるようですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:23.33,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:559497,563334}I'm afraid it'll be difficult to locate a single Nargacuga in here.{NOTE:ここで一頭のナルガクルガを捜し出すのは難しくありませんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:25.83,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:564877,565836}Perhaps…{NOTE:もし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.42,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:567213,570424}…my kinship with him isn't fully gone yet.{NOTE:俺とあいつにまだ絆がつながっているなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:33.96,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:572927,573969}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.34,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:576388,577348}Nargacuga!{NOTE:ナルガクルガ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.56,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:583646,584563}It's no use…{NOTE:駄目か…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.98,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:585523,587983}He may just be somewhere else.{NOTE:この辺りにはいないのかもしれませんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.11,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:589693,591112}I hope you're right.{NOTE:それだったらいいけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.28,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:592738,595282}Since we're already here…{NOTE:せっかくここまで来たんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.78,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:595282,597785}…why don't we look for some clues regarding the Ebon Riders?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズの手掛かりを探しませんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.07,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:598619,600079}Good idea.{NOTE:そうだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.24,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:600079,601247}Let's look around.{NOTE:調べてみよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:03.87,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:603040,603874}What was that?{NOTE:今のは!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:06.87,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:606127,606877}Ah!{NOTE:あっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.05,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:612341,614051}Nargacuga!{NOTE:ナルガクルガ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:14.88,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:614051,614885}It's you?{NOTE:お前か!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.47,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:619390,621475}It looks really agitated!{NOTE:すごく凶暴ですよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.51,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:621475,623519}Are you sure it's your Monstie, Cheval?{NOTE:本当にシュヴァルさんのオトモンですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:25.98,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:624645,625980}Yes.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:26.98,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:625980,626981}No doubt about it.{NOTE:間違いない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.02,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:631277,633028}I'm sorry for that time.{NOTE:あのときはごめん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.57,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:637533,638576}Ah.{NOTE:あっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.41,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:638576,639410}Cheval!{NOTE:シュヴァルさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:47.25,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:644206,647251}I really regret my behavior.{NOTE:お前にひどいことをして悪かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.50,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:652298,653507}Sorry.{NOTE:ごめんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.05,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:658429,659054}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.49,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:678449,680492}It's gone.{NOTE:行ってしまいましたよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.87,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:682328,684872}It's only natural that he hates me.{NOTE:あいつが俺のことを恨んでいるのは当然だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.00,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:686832,689001}I'm all right with it.{NOTE:絆が結べなくてもいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.00,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:690252,693005}I'm glad just knowing that he's still alive.{NOTE:生きていることが分かっただけでもいいんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.25,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:695174,696258}I see…{NOTE:そうですか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.47,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:703557,706477}We just can't seem to find the Ebon Riders, do we?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズ見つかりませんね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:48.81,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:707978,708812}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:52.48,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:710731,712483}What about the rest?{NOTE:他の皆さんはどうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.86,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:713859,714860}Wish I knew.{NOTE:どうだろうな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.28,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:724245,726288}It's a good night for hunting.{NOTE:狩りにはいい夜だねぇ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.25,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:730501,731252}A prey?{NOTE:獲物かい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.00,Beast,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732002,734004}{\an1\pos(80,180)\fad(0,400)}Purple Water Beast\NPurple Ludroth{NOTE:紫水獣ロアルドロス亜種}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.96,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:735464,737967}A Purple Ludroth?{NOTE:ロアルドロス亜種？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:22.01,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:737967,742012}I hoped it would be something more interesting.{NOTE:もうちょい歯応えのあるやつじゃないと面白くないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:33.10,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:749436,753107}But I guess I'll play with you for a bit\Nafter that introduction.{NOTE:でも向こうがやるってんなら相手してやらないとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.70,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:763200,765703}I'll play with you a lot!{NOTE:たっぷりかわいがってやるよ！}
